1
00:01:32,800 --> 00:01:33,560
This is the recipe

2
00:01:33,560 --> 00:01:34,320
your mother left you

3
00:01:34,320 --> 00:01:35,979
for that... whatever pastry.

4
00:01:36,120 --> 00:01:37,580
It's the black tea pastry.

5
00:01:40,960 --> 00:01:43,680
Pound the black tea a hundred times into fine powder.

6
00:01:43,680 --> 00:01:45,280
Refine the butter from milk.

7
00:01:45,360 --> 00:01:47,080
Four taels of butter,

8
00:01:47,080 --> 00:01:48,479
three mace of tea powder.

9
00:01:48,560 --> 00:01:50,620
Mix with flour and fold it nine times.

10
00:01:50,640 --> 00:01:52,039
This is too complicated.

11
00:01:54,440 --> 00:01:56,520
When I watched my mother make black tea pastry before,

12
00:01:56,520 --> 00:01:57,960
it always seemed so easy.

13
00:01:58,440 --> 00:01:59,640
But when it's my turn,

14
00:02:00,120 --> 00:02:02,320
even following the recipe step by step,

15
00:02:02,680 --> 00:02:04,610
I still can't recreate that taste.

16
00:02:15,200 --> 00:02:16,200
So,

17
00:02:16,200 --> 00:02:17,720
this last piece of black tea pastry,

18
00:02:17,720 --> 00:02:19,250
I've been reluctant to eat.

19
00:02:19,800 --> 00:02:21,160
I'm afraid if I eat it,

20
00:02:21,160 --> 00:02:23,160
I'll never taste this flavor again.

21
00:02:28,240 --> 00:02:28,880
Look.

22
00:02:29,000 --> 00:02:30,120
It's been kept for so long,

23
00:02:30,120 --> 00:02:31,240
but it still has a rich milky aroma

24
00:02:31,240 --> 00:02:32,480
and fragrant tea scent.

25
00:02:32,480 --> 00:02:33,760
There's even

26
00:02:33,880 --> 00:02:35,800
a hint of pine firewood.

27
00:02:36,040 --> 00:02:37,840
Smell it if you don't believe me.

28
00:02:41,800 --> 00:02:42,600
Linglong.

29
00:02:42,880 --> 00:02:43,280
You...

30
00:02:43,640 --> 00:02:44,040
I...

31
00:02:44,040 --> 00:02:45,520
My sense of smell is back!

32
00:02:51,960 --> 00:02:52,880
The tea aroma is rich,

33
00:02:52,880 --> 00:02:54,000
like flowers and honey.

34
00:02:54,000 --> 00:02:54,720
Good tea.

35
00:02:55,560 --> 00:02:56,320
Miss.

36
00:03:01,320 --> 00:03:02,040
Uncle Zhao.

37
00:03:02,120 --> 00:03:03,040
It stinks!

38
00:03:07,280 --> 00:03:08,520
I just went to the latrine

39
00:03:08,520 --> 00:03:10,120
and emptied the dung bucket.

40
00:03:14,720 --> 00:03:16,040
Miss has regained her sense of smell!

41
00:03:16,040 --> 00:03:16,600
Miss,

42
00:03:16,600 --> 00:03:18,130
your sense of smell is back!

43
00:03:58,400 --> 00:03:59,600
Rock bone resonance,

44
00:03:59,600 --> 00:04:00,600
osmanthus notes,

45
00:04:01,120 --> 00:04:02,380
and bamboo leaf scent.

46
00:04:02,560 --> 00:04:04,480
Fermented fifty to sixty percent,

47
00:04:04,480 --> 00:04:06,010
double rolled and roasted.

48
00:04:06,360 --> 00:04:07,600
This is Wuyi Rock Tea.

49
00:04:15,000 --> 00:04:16,260
A cold chestnut aroma.

50
00:04:16,920 --> 00:04:18,120
Steady and subtle,

51
00:04:18,519 --> 00:04:20,980
it should be slowly baked over a gentle fire.

52
00:04:21,040 --> 00:04:22,570
This is Huangshan Maofeng.

53
00:04:25,680 --> 00:04:26,640
Without a single mistake.

54
00:04:26,640 --> 00:04:27,840
Completely correct.

55
00:05:11,040 --> 00:05:11,880
Linglong.

56
00:05:12,360 --> 00:05:14,440
It's a pity my body is practically useless,

57
00:05:14,440 --> 00:05:16,200
otherwise I could lend you a hand.

58
00:05:16,200 --> 00:05:16,960
Oh, you.

59
00:05:17,160 --> 00:05:18,680
Just rest and regain your strength for now.

60
00:05:18,680 --> 00:05:19,880
When it comes to planning and calculating later,

61
00:05:19,880 --> 00:05:21,010
I'll need your help.

62
00:05:28,760 --> 00:05:29,480
Qiao Xin.

63
00:05:30,120 --> 00:05:31,450
I haven't asked you yet.

64
00:05:31,880 --> 00:05:34,200
Why do you know so much about the way of tea?

65
00:05:34,200 --> 00:05:36,080
I've studied the way of tea for decades.

66
00:05:36,080 --> 00:05:38,920
The techniques and methods you mentioned,

67
00:05:38,920 --> 00:05:40,650
even I have never heard of them.

68
00:05:41,080 --> 00:05:42,520
Do you immortals

69
00:05:42,920 --> 00:05:43,960
plant tea too?

70
00:05:46,400 --> 00:05:47,080
Yes.

71
00:05:47,360 --> 00:05:49,120
We immortals drink tea too.

72
00:05:51,120 --> 00:05:53,000
What is the tea in heaven like?

73
00:05:53,000 --> 00:05:53,930
Tell me about it.

74
00:05:55,640 --> 00:05:57,600
The tea we plant in heaven...

75
00:05:57,800 --> 00:05:59,080
Our tea leaves

76
00:05:59,320 --> 00:06:00,650
are grown in the clouds.

77
00:06:01,080 --> 00:06:02,480
The immortal boys and girls,

78
00:06:02,480 --> 00:06:04,360
after picking the tea leaves,

79
00:06:04,560 --> 00:06:06,890
will send them to a huge magical artifact.

80
00:06:07,760 --> 00:06:09,000
In just a short while,

81
00:06:09,360 --> 00:06:11,090
the fermented tea can be ready.

82
00:06:12,000 --> 00:06:12,840
Besides,

83
00:06:12,840 --> 00:06:14,000
drinking our tea

84
00:06:14,280 --> 00:06:15,810
can even make you immortal.

85
00:06:16,560 --> 00:06:17,040
Really?

86
00:06:18,760 --> 00:06:19,200
Oh,

87
00:06:19,200 --> 00:06:20,040
Linglong,

88
00:06:20,200 --> 00:06:21,560
if I were to explain everything in detail,

89
00:06:21,560 --> 00:06:23,080
I could talk for a whole day and night.

90
00:06:23,080 --> 00:06:24,540
The top priority right now

91
00:06:24,560 --> 00:06:26,280
is to improve the black tea first,

92
00:06:26,280 --> 00:06:28,680
and prepare for the Western tea exhibition in three months.

93
00:06:28,680 --> 00:06:30,000
Once it's done,

94
00:06:30,120 --> 00:06:32,320
I'll tell you as much as you want to hear.

95
00:06:32,600 --> 00:06:33,330
Fair enough.

96
00:06:33,680 --> 00:06:36,400
This way, there is hope for the improvement of Keemun black tea.

97
00:06:36,400 --> 00:06:38,920
And I won't have let my mother down with what she entrusted to me in the letter.

98
00:06:38,920 --> 00:06:41,580
You can also go back to heaven and be an immortal.

99
00:06:51,720 --> 00:06:52,920
Your Excellency Ito.

100
00:06:52,920 --> 00:06:53,780
Yamamoto-san.

101
00:06:54,120 --> 00:06:54,600
Yes.

102
00:06:55,200 --> 00:06:56,640
Welcome to Shanghai.

103
00:06:57,760 --> 00:06:58,420
Have a seat.

104
00:06:58,600 --> 00:06:59,040
Yes.

105
00:07:01,400 --> 00:07:02,560
I heard

106
00:07:02,560 --> 00:07:03,800
that you have obtained

107
00:07:03,800 --> 00:07:05,520
the formula for Keemun black tea.

108
00:07:05,520 --> 00:07:06,040
Yes.

109
00:07:06,560 --> 00:07:07,560
This is it.

110
00:07:18,360 --> 00:07:19,360
Yamamoto-san.

111
00:07:19,880 --> 00:07:20,320
Yes.

112
00:07:20,600 --> 00:07:22,080
You did a great job.

113
00:07:23,280 --> 00:07:25,560
Please analyze and research it as soon as possible,

114
00:07:25,560 --> 00:07:28,080
to make our own Japanese black tea.

115
00:07:28,520 --> 00:07:31,650
Find a formula that is more popular in the global market.

116
00:07:31,880 --> 00:07:34,960
If we suppress China's tea economy,

117
00:07:34,960 --> 00:07:36,680
it will help us win the holy war

118
00:07:36,680 --> 00:07:38,680
and realize the Greater East Asia Co-Prosperity Sphere,

119
00:07:38,680 --> 00:07:40,560
adding another weight to our side.

120
00:07:40,560 --> 00:07:41,840
The Great Japanese Empire

121
00:07:41,840 --> 00:07:43,840
will not forget your contribution.

122
00:07:43,840 --> 00:07:44,880
We have

123
00:07:44,880 --> 00:07:47,210
the world's most advanced laboratories,

124
00:07:47,480 --> 00:07:48,640
and the world's

125
00:07:48,640 --> 00:07:50,000
best talents.

126
00:07:51,080 --> 00:07:53,010
We will definitely not disappoint

127
00:07:53,080 --> 00:07:55,210
Your Excellency Ito's expectations.

128
00:07:55,840 --> 00:07:58,159
Of course I believe in Mr. Yamamoto.

129
00:07:58,600 --> 00:08:01,060
With the power of our Great Japanese Empire,

130
00:08:01,160 --> 00:08:03,680
what else is impossible?

131
00:08:04,160 --> 00:08:05,680
Even unifying East Asia

132
00:08:06,000 --> 00:08:07,520
is only a matter of time.

133
00:08:08,200 --> 00:08:09,880
What we hold in our hands

134
00:08:10,160 --> 00:08:11,880
must be the most advanced and best

135
00:08:11,880 --> 00:08:14,000
in all of East Asia.

136
00:08:14,960 --> 00:08:16,280
If not,

137
00:08:17,240 --> 00:08:19,080
then we will stop at nothing

138
00:08:19,080 --> 00:08:20,240
to snatch it

139
00:08:20,240 --> 00:08:21,400
from elsewhere.

140
00:08:23,160 --> 00:08:25,400
Since ancient times, Japan

141
00:08:25,400 --> 00:08:27,560
has suffered from resource scarcity

142
00:08:28,080 --> 00:08:29,940
and frequent natural disasters.

143
00:08:30,320 --> 00:08:32,039
This treasured land of China,

144
00:08:33,400 --> 00:08:35,400
we are bound to get it.

145
00:08:36,679 --> 00:08:37,520
Remember,

146
00:08:39,480 --> 00:08:40,320
history

147
00:08:40,760 --> 00:08:43,440
belongs to the victors,

148
00:08:44,360 --> 00:08:46,280
not the losers.

149
00:08:47,600 --> 00:08:48,720
Your Excellency Ito,

150
00:08:48,720 --> 00:08:50,180
you are absolutely right.

151
00:08:51,080 --> 00:08:53,280
I heard that in three months,

152
00:08:53,280 --> 00:08:54,880
the exposition will be held.

153
00:08:55,720 --> 00:08:58,760
This is the best opportunity to step on the Chinese

154
00:08:59,560 --> 00:09:01,120
and make Japanese tea

155
00:09:01,120 --> 00:09:04,400
world-famous.

156
00:09:06,440 --> 00:09:06,920
Yes.

157
00:09:23,160 --> 00:09:24,690
Hu Wenyi has been executed.

158
00:09:24,720 --> 00:09:25,920
You can rest in peace

159
00:09:25,920 --> 00:09:27,050
in the netherworld.

160
00:09:35,000 --> 00:09:35,480
Miss.

161
00:09:35,840 --> 00:09:37,760
Xu Zhinian has sent you a letter.

162
00:09:58,880 --> 00:10:00,400
Dear Linglong,

163
00:10:00,400 --> 00:10:01,840
The coastal frontiers are in crisis,

164
00:10:01,840 --> 00:10:03,200
and the flames of war rise like mountains.

165
00:10:03,200 --> 00:10:05,040
Yet in the dead of night,

166
00:10:05,040 --> 00:10:06,560
I miss you deeply.

167
00:10:06,560 --> 00:10:08,960
Your face and voice appear right before my eyes.

168
00:10:08,960 --> 00:10:10,280
Please take good care of yourself,

169
00:10:10,280 --> 00:10:11,760
and do not worry about me.

170
00:10:11,760 --> 00:10:13,160
Once the enemies are driven out,

171
00:10:13,160 --> 00:10:14,440
I will return safely,

172
00:10:14,440 --> 00:10:16,280
honoring our parting promise.

173
00:10:16,560 --> 00:10:19,480
Enclosed with this letter is an armor button,

174
00:10:19,480 --> 00:10:21,880
something I wear close to my skin day and night.

175
00:10:21,880 --> 00:10:23,080
Though the ocean waves are fierce,

176
00:10:23,080 --> 00:10:24,360
this button is like my heart,

177
00:10:24,360 --> 00:10:25,920
forever steadfast and unwavering.

178
00:10:25,920 --> 00:10:27,560
Yours, Zhinian.
